Preheat the oven to 425Â°F. On a rimmed baking sheet, toss the carrots with the oil, salt, and red pepper or cayenne. Spread them out in a single layer. Roast for 15 minutes, stir well, and roast for 10 more minutes. Then remove from the oven and drizzle with the pomegranate molasses; toss gently to coat the carrots with the molasses. Roast util the carrots are golden and soft, about 5 more minutes. Serve garnished with cilantro.